concept.title: IEC 61850 Reality Modular Inverter List

othermeta.name: title
othermeta.content: IEC 61850 Reality Modular Inverter List CPT DD00551825

othermeta.name: shortdesc
othermeta.content: List of Reality modular inverter modules and IEC 61850 mappings for inverter control and monitoring.

conbody.p: The default logical device (LD) for all IEC tags for Reality Modular Inverter is “i61GMODACUPS_LD1”.

The IEC tag path format is LN$FC$DO$DA.
Logical node (LN)
Functional constraint (FC)
Data object (DO)
Data attribute (DA)
